import React from "react"; import { Container, Grid, Typography, Table, TableHead, TableRow, TableCell, TableBody, } from "@mui/material"; import DashboardCard from "../components/DashboardCard"; import useFetch from "./useFetch"; import "./Dashboard.css"; export default function Dashboard() { const [health] = useFetch("/api/v1/health", { status: "..." }); const [students] = useFetch("/api/v1/students", []); const [attendance] = useFetch("/api/v1/attendance", []); const studentsCount = Array.isArray(students) ? students.length : "--"; const attendancePct = Array.isArray(attendance) && studentsCount > 0 ? `${Math.round((attendance.length / Math.max(1, studentsCount)) * 100)}%` : "--"; return ( Smart University Admin Dashboard {/* Recent Attendance Table */} Latest Attendance Records
Student Method Location Timestamp {attendance .slice(0, 10) .map(({ id, student_id, method, location, timestamp }) => ( {student_id} {method} {location} {new Date(timestamp).toLocaleString()} ))}
